  <brief_title>Importance of the GH/IGF-1 Axis for Human Substrate and Energy Metabolism During Calorie Restriction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Importance of the GH/IGF-1 Axis for Human Substrate and Energy Metabolism During Calorie Restriction</official_title>
